            : 'tis also observable, that when they were ready to go out, he desired her to bring her Wedding Ring with her. His Master the Vintner Witnessed, That he gave him leave to go out that Day, and that he went from home about Two in the After-noon, and came not Home till Seven at Night, and then in a very great Heat, and like a discomposed Person. 
               <persName id="t16840702-6-person28">
                  Sarah 
                  Miller
               <interp inst="t16840702-6-person28" type="surname" value="Miller"></interp>
